Package bacnet.scripts.listeriomics.nterm

Class NTermStat

java.lang.Object
bacnet.scripts.listeriomics.nterm.NTermStat
public class NTermStat extends Object
List of method to do statistics about common features in N-Terminus of genes: - start codon - SD binding - AU proportion - Folding energy
Author:
UIBC

      @Deprecated public int getUTRLength(Gene gene)
      Deprecated.
      For each gene search the closest TSS downstream, and return the UTR length (=distance between gene and TSS) We don't start at the start codon but -20bp, in case there is a TSS in this region indicating a possible short UTR with alternative aTIS

      public static void statInternalORF(Genome genome)
